paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: Extracted pathogenic variant information for the BRCA2 gene, including penetrance data.

functional_data.summary: The BRCA2 variants are associated with a high risk of breast cancer.

variants.additional_notes: Four of the BRCA2 variants have previously been detected in more than one Finnish BC family.
key_quotes: In more detail, 8/1356 (0.6%) patients had a BRCA1 and 16/1356 (1.2%) had a BRCA2 variant.

extraction_metadata.notes: Only one BRCA2 variant was reported in the paper.
